channel.title: Need help to get my server online
channel.description:
Hello all :) Me and my friends decided to make a server ourself This is my server i EVER made (Since im the smartest one i had to make it :D ) But i found out that my server wouldnt get online .. And Yes i do have the NO-IP file running
First of all , i used this source : [URL=http://rapidshare.com/files/19559819/EarthScape_PKZ_V.1.rar.html]Eartschape PKZ V1[/URL] This tutorial : [URL=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,200036.0.html]http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,200036.0.html[/URL]
When i run the "Runserver.bat" file it says this : "Starting EarthScape PKZ Server on 0.0.0.0:43594" When it should be this (i think) : "Starting HeavenScape on heavenspk.no-ip.info"(I'm NOT advertising) Picture of the Screen : [IMG]http://img453.imageshack.us/img453/6884/errorshowzt2.png[/img]
Does anyone know how to change it or how to put the server online ? I would appreciate it ! Thanks.

This is what i did :
I made a “Scrabbling-Pad”(Dont know if thats correct english oO)
I copied this in it :

@echo off title Gazmask's Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_03\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java pause

And if so , could you show me where to put it ?
Since im not so good in english and this is my first server ever XD
Thanks in Advance[br][size=1]Posted on: October 28, 2007, 02:26:57 PM[/size][hr]Oke now , i found out a lot of things XD
I had to right click it and Edit it …
First i had a JRE Java so i download a JDK one
Now another problem has appeared
I noticed i couldnt find a file named javac.exe in my Java file but what i did find was a javaw.exe
So i tried to put that in and it says “Could not find the main class.Program will exit.”

If this helps any , i used this code :

@echo off title HeavenScape Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_03\bin\javaw.exe" -cp . *.java pause
If this is right then i guess im screwed
If not i hope someone would help me
